# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# dependencies (ignore in all folders)
**/node_modules/
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.*
**/.yarn/*
!**/.yarn/patches
!**/.yarn/plugins
!**/.yarn/releases
!**/.yarn/versions
**/.vscode/

.turbo/

# testing (all folders)
**/coverage/

# next.js (all folders)
**/.next/
**/out/

# production (all folders)
**/build/

# misc
.DS_Store
*.pem

# debug
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
.env*

# vercel (all folders)
**/.vercel/

# supabase
/supabase/

# typescript
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts
